            "title": "港股曾跌410點  光伏及蘋概股捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股中段跌幅擴大，最多曾挫410點或1.58%，報25478，現跌334點或1.29%，報25554。      </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌122點或1.32%，報9132點 ;  恒生國企指數跌125點或2.09%，報5878點。   </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1289.64億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義光能(00968)挫5.44%，報3.48元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 協鑫科技(03800)跌5.8%，報1.3元 ; 福萊特玻璃(06865)跌4.07%，報11.08元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">手機設備股跑輸大市，比亞迪電子(00285)跌5.31%，報38.86元，跌居藍籌股第二位 ; 舜宇光學科技(02382)跌2.49%，報78.35元，丘鈦科技(01478)瀉7.62%，報13.83元，高偉電子(01415)跌5.12%，報31.48元。蘋果公司傳計劃於2026年底或2027年初推出配備觸控螢幕的升級版MacBook Pro，將放棄喬布斯反對豎直觸控螢幕電腦的立場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15349615-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c410%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%89%e4%bc%8f%e5%8f%8a%e8%98%8b%e6%a6%82%e8%82%a1%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 11:10:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
