            "title": "港股開跌36點   金礦股揚升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌36點或0.14%，報25821，恒生國企指數開報9259點，無升跌，恒生科技指數開跌4點或0.07%，報5999。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交26.66億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20241017_CR_source-licensed_gold_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20241017_CR_source-licensed_gold_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蔚來(09866)升5.62%，報52.05元，昨曾急跌13%，據報遭GIC起訴收入不實。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金黃金國際(02559)升2.1%，報150.5元 ; 紫金(02899)升5.39%，報34.8元。山東黃金(01787)升4.97%，報39.68元 ; 招金(01818)升3.3%，報33.44元；赤峰黃金(06693)升4%，報33.96元；靈寶黃金(03330)升3.1%，報20.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">協鑫科技(03800)升4.35%，報1.44元 ; 信義光能(00968)升1.09%，報3.7元。</p>\n</div>",
